{"id":"kiss","term":"Kiss","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Of affection (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 27:26\">Gen. 27:26</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 1:27\">27</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 29:13\">29:13</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 7:38\">Luke 7:38</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 7:45\">45</a>); reconciliation (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 33:4\">Gen. 33:4</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 14:33\">2 Sam. 14:33</a>); leave-taking (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 31:28\">Gen. 31:28</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 31:55\">55</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ruth 1:14\">Ruth 1:14</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 19:39\">2 Sam. 19:39</a>); homage (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 2:12\">Ps. 2:12</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 10:1\">1 Sam. 10:1</a>); spoken of as between parents and children (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 27:26\">Gen. 27:26</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 31:28\">31:28</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 31:55\">55</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 48:10\">48:10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 50:1\">50:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 18:7\">Ex. 18:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ruth 1:9\">Ruth 1:9</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ruth 1:14\">14</a>); between male relatives (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 29:13\">Gen. 29:13</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 33:4\">33:4</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 45:15\">45:15</a>). It accompanied social worship as a symbol of brotherly love (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 16:16\">Rom. 16:16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 16:20\">1 Cor. 16:20</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Corinthians 13:12\">2 Cor. 13:12</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Thessalonians 5:26\">1 Thess. 5:26</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Peter 5:14\">1 Pet. 5:14</a>). The worship of idols was by kissing the image or the hand toward the image (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 19:18\">1 Kings 19:18</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hosea 13:2\">Hos. 13:2</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 27:26","Genesis 1:27","Genesis 29:13","Luke 7:38","Luke 7:45","Genesis 33:4","2 Samuel 14:33","Genesis 31:28","Genesis 31:55","Ruth 1:14","2 Samuel 19:39","Psalms 2:12","1 Samuel 10:1","Genesis 48:10","Genesis 50:1","Exodus 18:7","Ruth 1:9","Genesis 45:15","Romans 16:16","1 Corinthians 16:20","2 Corinthians 13:12","1 Thessalonians 5:26","1 Peter 5:14","1 Kings 19:18","Hosea 13:2"]}